Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 20:04:27 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] ADD terminal visual selection for focused-pane copy
 workflows

Terminal command mode supports character, line, and block selections in the focused pane so users can copy visible chat or agent-list text with vim-style yanks. The terminal app emits a single OSC 52 clipboard sequence per yank and records a concise copy notice.
